if statements => conditional statements

- control flow: execute logic based on the condition statements
- if/else statements

- if (condition)
    logic to be executed
  elseif (second condition)
    logic to be executed
  elseif (second condition)
    logic to be executed
  else
    logic to be executed
  end
  
  #speak_to_grandma << looking for an instance method
  
  def method_name
  
  end 